    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready to hit the road with a new owner who will love it as much as I have. You seriously won't find another one this clean. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
