    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available now is an exceptional 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, preserved in collector-grade condition. This A80 chassis retains its original 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant, featuring the factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and a pristine iron block. The drivetrain is anchored by the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox, feeding power to a Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the double-wishbone suspension remains tight with no bushing degradation, and the cooling system maintains perfect thermal efficiency. The engine bay is concours-ready, showing original VIN tags and factory-spec torque stripes on critical fasteners. With a flawless undercarriage and zero oxidation on the aluminum subframes, this is a rare, unmodified example of JDM engineering at its peak.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
