    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
