    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is a mechanical masterpiece, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The double VANOS system has been fully serviced with upgraded seals and rattle kits, ensuring optimal cam timing across the entire rev range. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings replaced with VAC coated bearings, addressing all chassis and internal engine vulnerabilities. The suspension utilizes fresh OEM bushings and dampers to maintain the factory-intended kinematics and turn-in crispness. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine interior, this M3 exhibits zero hydraulic leaks and a factory-tight limited-slip differential. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
